This product bundles third-party open-source tools within its Docker images
to perform SBOM generation and analysis. Those tools are separate programs,
invoked at arm's length (as separate processes), and remain under their own
respective licenses. A full inventory of bundled tools, their licenses, and
the corresponding source locations is provided in THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md.

The base image (ghcr.io/sktelecom/sbom-scanner) bundles only permissively
licensed tools (Apache-2.0 / MIT). GPL-licensed tools, when used, are isolated
in a separate opt-in image (ghcr.io/sktelecom/sbom-scanner-firmware); see
THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md for the GPL source offer.
